      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for daily commuting. While it is mechanically sound and has been consistently serviced, the exterior shows visible signs of age including some scratches and minor door dings. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows moderate wear from regular use. It is a solid, functional choice for someone looking for a dependable car without the premium price of a newer model.",
