    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is looking for a new home and someone with a vision. It's in rougher condition and will definitely need some mechanical and cosmetic attention to get it back to its best, but it offers a great foundation for a dedicated project. If you're looking for an affordable entry point and aren't afraid to roll up your sleeves, this is the one for you!",
      "price": 6500.0,
